{"tid":914250,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"分析師預測：《CyberPunk 2077》發售首季銷量有望達1900萬份","createTime":"2018-11-24T06:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T08:50:58.000Z","uid":66943,"like":16,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"266906277c0e9719b69810de4272f840553ed530","tid":914250,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"波蘭的股票經紀公司Vestor DM認為《CyberPunk 2077》有望成為像《Red Dead Redemption II》那樣的銷售怪獸，《Red Dead Redemption II》在短短三天銷售額就突破了7億美元，分析師預測《CyberPunk 2077》首季銷量可能會高達1900萬套。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEhawpT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEhawpT.jpg&h=44659a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　Vestor DM考慮到《Red Dead Redemption II》只在主機平台上發售，而《CyberPunk 2077》同時在PC和主機平台發售，並且《CyberPunk 2077》的科幻風格相比《The Witcher 3》在西方更受大眾歡迎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2GuMYw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2GuMYw.jpg&h=1c76286c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　如果分析師預測成功，那麼《CyberPunk 2077》可能會成為史上最成功的RPG遊戲，雖然1900萬銷量還不如《Diablo 3》和《The Elder Scrolls V : Skyrim》，但已經接近《Fallout 4 》，並且遠超《Dragon Age》、《Mass Effect》；預測說的是發售首季銷量1900萬份，所以這個數字還可以繼續增長。當然，這一切的前提都建立在《CyberPunk 2077》的質素真的達到了玩家們心中的預期。"},{"pid":"6c1e80b0c11b9dde8197da7729d37dc291cb7315","tid":914250,"uid":82889,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"咁幾時出啊"},{"pid":"632f677f2b2f24ebf5c0d062903048c66294e158","tid":914250,"uid":61763,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"韋拿踢法似我"},{"pid":"036baf3c966a95c9a99fda6b553bcbd23133088f","tid":914250,"uid":51920,"like":14,"dislike":28,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:01:35.000Z","msg":"似 red 2 = 雷作"},{"pid":"863fab0d92c5cbe1c7d6de30e2e43a217e284b37","tid":914250,"uid":81192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:03:12.000Z","msg":"股票佬睇科技野預測多數都係燈"},{"pid":"3f9ff2e1c5a2f5ad78fa9ad2677b88bd982ff373","tid